<h1>So I hear you are wanting to feel happy. Well I guarentee, you'll be extremely happy after paying these spot a visit!</h1>
<p>Food always makes me happy! Below are some of my restaurant recommendations:</p>
<p></p>
<p>Head over to Doppio Zero for fresh and tasty Italian cuisine as well as their special Wine Tasting Saturdays! (My personal favorite is the Wood-Fried Puttanesca  Pizza!)</p>
<p>Address: 83 Rivonia Rd, Sandhurst, Sandton, 2196, South Africa</p>
<p></p>
<p>Check out O'Galitos for divine Portuguese and South African cuisine. My personal recommendation is the Grilled Salmon.</p>
<p>Address: 1303 Heuwel Rd, Centurion Central, Centurion, 0157, South Africa</p>
